WEBVTT

00:00:55.774 --> 00:01:01.605
they were like, "Hey, we would love it
if you would be our guest

00:01:01.629 --> 00:01:03.123
in the psych ward."

00:01:03.147 --> 00:01:08.020
(Laughter)

00:01:08.597 --> 00:01:13.644
We joked that her suicide
would have made a way better postcard.

00:01:13.668 --> 00:01:14.726
(Laughter)

00:01:14.750 --> 00:01:16.134
We talked shop.

00:01:16.448 --> 00:01:17.870
(Laughter)

00:01:17.894 --> 00:01:20.353
She allowed me to be deeply depressed

00:01:20.377 --> 00:01:25.170
and have a genuine connection
to another person, simultaneously.

00:01:25.789 --> 00:01:26.947
For the first time,

00:01:26.971 --> 00:01:30.145
I identified as somebody
living with depression,